title: 189. Andy & DJ CTI: Paul Vs. Woodley 2, San Francisco Restaurant Denying Service To Cops & Jussie Smollett Testimony
itunes:title: 189. Andy & DJ CTI: Paul Vs. Woodley 2, San Francisco Restaurant Denying Service To Cops & Jussie Smollett Testimony
description: "Fuck you, LeBron' - Kyle Rittenhouse. In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss the rematch between Jake Paul & Tyron Woodley, a San Francisco restaurant refusing to service on-duty police officers, and Empire actor Jussie Smollett's testimony in court claiming the attack was not a 'hoax.'
